memsdk-letta

This project is an independent interoperability implementation of the
memsdk Supermemory-compatible interface, backed by Letta memory.

Supermemory is a trademark of its respective owner. Letta is a trademark
of its respective owner. This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by,
or sponsored by either company.

The memsdk interface specification is derived from the public TypeScript
type surface of the supermemory npm package (v4.24.12), used solely for
the purpose of achieving TypeScript interface compatibility.
